title: Awesome Kids and Beginners Cycling Workout...  Rollers, Static Trainer or Even Stabilisers!
description:
Hi all you awesome kids.... here is my first cycling exercise video...

Here is Stage 1 of Tour De Kids....

You can do it on rollers... a turbo trainer..... or even just put shoes under your stabilisers....

If you like it please let me know on Instagram at @rubywisaac and I will do another one...

Oh and mind out for those ducks!!!!!

Stay awesome!!!!


Ruby X
channelDescription: Hi, I'm the little cyclist from Little Big Shots. I'm an 16 year old cyclist from the UK. I am also known as Race Reporter.  There is all kinds of fun stuff on my channel from interviewing riders, to some cool tricks on rollers.... I am also making my kids cycling show too..... Hopefully you will enjoy them..... Ruby X
